00:38:18,050 --> 00:38:19,320
Ya.

362
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:21,310
Mengapa?

363
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:23,570
Aku tidak tahu?

364
00:38:23,570 --> 00:38:27,040
Xiao Bai. Nak, kau telah jadi pembohong sejak kau kecil.

365
00:38:27,040 --> 00:38:29,880
